snippet.title: Punchimals Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Punchimals is an online and local physics-based fighting game for 1-4 players set in a world where cute, chubby animals settle their differences by duking it out in giant mechs

Due to a lack of exercise (certainly not caused by overuse of mechs in everyday life), obesity and mech combat has ravaged the globe!

Wishlist Punchimals: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2360970
